=E2=80=9Cissues=E2=80=9D that will likely confront the New Paramount, inclu=
ding his view that =E2=80=9Cbetter tech alone cannot save Paramount,=E2=80=
=9D as the Ellisons have been trumpeting since they inked the deal earlier =
this week. =E2=80=9CWhile we love that Skydance is committed to investing h=
eavily in tech to transform
Paramount, it is important to realize that Skydance has never built, nor ru=
