d have also signaled, to the tune of another $2 billion. =E2=80=9CChanging =
that behavior will not be easy and requires tremendous amounts of content v=
s. an episode a week that you watch for 22-44 minutes,=E2=80=9D he wrote, w=
hile adding that =E2=80=9CParamount=E2=80=99s content coffers are pretty un=
derwhelming. =E2=80=A6 The need for far more content is glaringly obvious.=
